node.text:
I made a tiktok video about my PCOS & I’ve been flooded with DMs about how I cleared my skin & deal with my symptoms. I figured it would be easier to just sit down and chat about my whole experience. I didn’t feel it was necessary to make this a whole production with edits so enjoy me rambling on for 10 minutes. I want to be as real as I can with y’all. I will still respond to all the DMs that I can. I hope this helps & please message me with any other questions. If you’re struggling right now, I PROMISE it will get better 💓💞
Thank you to @esthylexi for changing my life & helping me get my skin back! #pcos #pcosawareness #pcosfighter #acnepositivity #skincare #skincaretips

node.text: We know breastfeeding can be challenging. Especially trying to find that perfect position for you and baby. It was difficult trying to sit comfortably while Poppy was trying to get the perfect latch. Luckily, I found the @fridamom Adjustable Nursing Pillow! It has removeable layers to help you find the right height from lap to latch. Thank you #fridamom for making our nursing sessions more comfortable ❤️#fridababy

node.text:
Im currently 2 months postpartum & hair shedding/thinning is getting real! Hair shredding is a normal postpartum experience caused by a shift in hormones after birth. Seeing your hair fall out during an already stressful and overwhelming time in your life is scary! But we no longer have to worry, @nutrafol Postpartum is an OBGYN developed natural hair supplement specifically formulated for the needs of women during postpartum shedding and helps grow healthier hair! It’s so easy to incorporate into your crazy mom life routine. Now, everyone’s postpartum experience is different! Results vary, but generally you’ll see improvements within the first 3-6 months! 🙌🏻 

I am NOT letting my postpartum hair shedding get me down! All my mommas out there experiencing hair thinning, you are not alone and we can do this together with Nutrafol Postpartum! Head on over to my stories and swipe up to get $50 off your first 3 months subscription! Join me on this hair growth journey! #nutrafol #nutrafolpartner
